<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>PointBlank Notifications</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background:linear-gradient(45deg,rgb(189, 163, 189), white)
        }
        .container {
            display: flex;
            margin-bottom: 1px;
            height:100vh;
        }
        .notifications {
            flex: 1;
            padding: 20px;
            border-right: 2px solid black;
        }
        .description {
            flex: 1;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .notification-item {
            margin-bottom: 17px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }
        .notification-item h3 {
            margin: 0 0 10px 0;
        }
        .notification-item p {
            margin: 0;
        }
        .icon {
            margin-left: 10px;
            font-size: 24px; 
            color:yellow; 
        }
        h1 {
            background-color: rgb(40, 2, 40);
            color: white;
            padding: 8px;
            font-weight: bolder;
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: -7px;
        }
        .back {
            background-color: rgb(40, 2, 40);
            text-decoration: none;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            border: none;
            margin-top: 10px;
            margin-left: 525px;
        }
        a {
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 20px;
            color:white;
        }
    </style>
    <!-- <link rel="stylesheet" href="/club.css">  -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0-beta3/css/all.min.css">
</head>
<body>
    <h1>PointBlank Notifications</h1>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="notifications">
            <ol>
                <% notifications.sort((a, b) => new Date(b.date) - new Date(a.date)).forEach((notification, index) => { %>
                    <li class="notification-item">
                        <div>
                            <h3><%= notification.message %></h3>
                            <p>Date: <%= new Date(notification.date).toLocaleDateString() %></p>
                        </div>
                        <% if (index === 0) { %> 
                            <i class="fas fa-star icon"></i> 
                        <% } %>
                    </li>
                <% }); %>
            </ol>
        </div>
        <div class="description">
            <h2>About PointBlank Club</h2>
            <h4>
                Point Blank has hosted 40+ editions of its PB Hustle coding contest, where participants tackle 5-7 progressively challenging questions in their chosen language. The aim is to improve college programming culture and qualify teams for ACM ICPC. Notably, DSCE's top programmers have emerged from this, with Codechef long challenge participation growing from 3 to 70+ participants.</h4>
            <h4>Point Blank has organised 100+ small and large workshops in topics ranging from open source, to devops, machine learning, placement scenarios, data structures and algorithms, mobile and web development among other things. Most of these workshops are conducted in an informal, unscripted way, though we do document some of our most important workshops. An example is our primer to F/OSS development</h4>
        </div>
    </div>
    <button class="back"> <a href="http://127.0.0.1:5501/club.html">Back to Club Page</a> </button>  
</body>
</html>
